PrecisAuthorization of the appointment of the HONOURABLE JULIUS ISAAC, a Justice of the Federal Court of Appeal, to serve on the Commission of Inquiry into the upsurge of criminal violence since May 2001 in a number of Jamaican urban communities, for a period commencing on March 1, 2002 and terminating on March 31, 2002.
Attachments
precis:
Authorization of the appointment of the HONOURABLE JULIUS ISAAC, a Justice
of the Federal Court of Appeal, to serve on the Commission of Inquiry into
the upsurge of criminal violence since May 2001 in a number of Jamaican
urban communities, for a period commencing on March 1, 2002 and
terminating on March 31, 2002.
